          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — generate articles for the same 30-keyword target list per tool.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — on-page score, indexing rate, ranked keywords after 90 days, total cost.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $1,640 across 10 tools, Mar–May 2026.</li>
